attributes.Long form description: First, the student grabs a bag of coffee beans and loads them into the hopper. The student grabs a cup and places it under the coffee dispenser. Then the student prepares a cup of coffee. The student adds cream to the coffee. The instructor asks the student to stir the coffee. Next, the student tells the instructor that he wants to wash the spoon. The student washes the spoon and then stirs the coffee. The student removes the drip tray. The student disassembles the parts of the drip tray. The student throws the leftover coffee in the sink. The student assembles the drip tray and places it back into the coffee machine.
